                    <p class="card-text">Committee delegation software for organizing assets, collecting payments, and delegating roles.</p>
                    <p class="card-text">GHOST uses this as a central hub as they prep for the upcoming tour season, and the website caters to ~ 30 - 50 individuals in this committee. </p>
                    <p class="card-text">This software improved their workflow by acting as a hub for collecting info, but also by automating the generation of spreadsheets with GHOST member contract data.</p>
                    <p class="card-text">Features also include being able to edit the content details in the website and delating permissions and roles.</p>
                    <a asp-area="" asp-controller="projects" asp-action="projects" asp-route-id="gig-harbor-open-studio-tour">

                        <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm mx-auto d-block">Take a Look</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
